<h1>Bel-Aire Calgary Real Estate and Homes for Sale</h1>
<p>If you are looking for a wealthy, upscale neighbourhood in southwest Calgary, you’ve found it! Bel-Aire is one of southwest Calgary’s most affluent neighbourhoods, made up of sprawling houses amid green spaces and parks and spectacular views of the mountains. </p>
<p>Bel-Aire is a small, close-knit, neighbourhood with unique luxury homes on gorgeous tree-lined streets. It is one of Calgary’s most sought-after neighbourhoods, given its proximity to all the necessary amenities. It is also a quiet and peaceful neighbourhood, with very little traffic passing through. </p>
