            <h2>Bel-Aire Real Estate Market</h2>
            <p>One of the wealthiest neighborhoods in south west Calgary, Bel-Aire is one of the most highly sought after residential communities among the affluent in the city. The community is located on the eastern edge of Glenmore Reservoir and to the west of the Meadowlark Park community.</p>
            <p>Ever since its development in the early sixties, the community in Bel-Aire has been home to some of the most influential families in town, not to mention the breathtaking views of the surrounding Rockies and downtown that result in the properties in the area getting lifted off the market like hot cakes. Homes for sale in Bel-Aire majorly comprise of single-family detached homes that are regularly available at an average price of around $2,750,000. With the Calgary Country Club golf course located only a stone’s throw away, the Bel-Aire Real estate offers abundant opportunities for the residents to stay engaged in their leisure hours.</p>
            <p>As of 2006, 100% of homes in Bel-Aire were single detached homes (one storey and multi-storey), with 5.4% being used for rental purposes </p>
        </div>
