            <h2>Bel-Aire Luxury Real Estate Listings</h2>
            <p>Calgary Real Estate Quadrant: SouthWest Calgary<br>Similar neighboring communities of <a href="/mayfair.php" target="_self">Mayfair</a>, <a href="/meadowlark-park.php" target="_self">Meadowlark Park</a>, <a href="/britannia.php" target="_self">Britannia</a> and <a href="/elboya.php" target="_self">Elboya</a>.<br>Community Established 1960<br><br>An exclusive community of luxury estates in Calgary, Bel-Aire is just east of the Glenmore Reservoir, in close proximity to the Glenmore Dam. Residents of the community of Bel-Aire access numerous recreational activities allowed by the closeness to Heritage Park, the Glenmore Reservoir, Calgary Golf and Country Club, and the Caglary bike pathway. This district of fine real estate boasts city views, overlooks the Glenmore Reservoir, the Elbow River Valley, and features amazing mountain views as well. The Rocky Mountains can also be enjoyed from the many open spaces in the area. The Calgary city center is located just north of Bel-Aire, via Elbow Drive.</p>
            <p>Bel-Aire is a luxurious community with a broad selection of luxury homes, all of which are detached single-family homes, prices being between the low million dollar to the high $2 million range.</p>
